{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Implement state hash comparison and N-block alignment check\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Build merge process for liquidity pools and Shapley histories\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Deploy on testnet with simulated fork/merge cycles\sa180\par}
