{\pard \qc \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 8. The Knowledge Primitive\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li720 \fi0 {\b \u8220"Forks are features, not threats. Economic gravity pulls toward coherence without forcing consensus. The root strengthens as the network grows.\u8221"}\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 This applies beyond protocol design: - {\b Open source}: Forks that maintain upstream compatibility strengthen the original project - {\b Markets}: Competition between similar products raises the baseline for all - {\b Evolution}: Speciation followed by convergence produces stronger organisms than either alone\par}
{\pard \qc \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\i VibeSwap is the sum of all its forks. The black hole pulls everything back.}\par}
